title: Tag Version 1
description:
The 'one series' of Antennae do not rely on user accounts and login; it's basically a wrapper around face/voice recognition services.
`v1`

title: Confirm basic rekognition collection actions
description: Make sure the collections shown in the app actually exist on AWS and CREATE/DELETE actions can properly be made.

milestone.title: 2.0.0 Release for AWS Social Good Hackathon
milestone.description:
We want to complete version 1.0.0 of Antennae in time to submit it for the DevPost AWS Hackathon
https://serverlessrepo.devpost.com/

>  Our Serverless Apps for Social Good hackathon invites you to publish serverless applications that can be used as stand-alone assets and/or as inputs that can be combined with other applications to add to the open-source serverless ecosystem and to support the work being done by developers and nonprofit organizations around the world. Creating a serverless application focused on ending trafficking is not required to be eligible to win category prizes, but it is required to be eligible to win the two related bonus prizes.

## Features
- 1:1 person to face mapping
- search multiple databases
- search all collections by default

title: Documentation for Infrastructure
description: Create README's for the `/infrastructure` directory and `/docker` directory.
